    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="4月11日"><a href="#4月11日" class="headerlink" title="4月11日"></a>4月11日</h2><p>我的生日。在经历了半年无所事事的大专生活后，这一天终于来了。<br>这半年里似乎学了很多东西（存疑），认识了很多新朋友（网上），也算是小有收获。<br>最近几天没更新，在做一个网页小游戏，准备参加一下b站的游戏开发活动。等生日过完回头把游戏开发心路补上。<br>至野蛮生长的19岁。<br><a href="https://www.liulibuliuli.com/">博客</a><br><a href="https://m.bilibili.com/space/1394337109">哔哩哔哩</a><br><a href="https://v.douyin.com/d8a2gs3Q-lw/">渲染作品</a><br>作品集：准备中…<br>This is an AI 游戏网页demo：开发中…</p><div class="fluid-custom-gallery">  <a class="fancybox" href="/img/post/过生日了喵/1.webp" data-fancybox="birthday-2026" data-caption="1.webp">    <img src="/img/post/过生日了喵/1.webp" alt="1.webp">  </a>  <a class="fancybox" href="/img/post/过生日了喵/2.webp" data-fancybox="birthday-2026" data-caption="2.webp">    <img src="/img/post/过生日了喵/2.webp" alt="2.webp">  </a>  <a class="fancybox" href="/img/post/过生日了喵/3.webp" data-fancybox="birthday-2026" data-caption="3.webp">    <img src="/img/post/过生日了喵/3.webp" alt="3.webp">  </a>  <a class="fancybox" href="/img/post/过生日了喵/4.webp" data-fancybox="birthday-2026" data-caption="4.webp">    <img src="/img/post/过生日了喵/4.webp" alt="4.webp">  </a>  <a class="fancybox" href="/img/post/过生日了喵/5.webp" data-fancybox="birthday-2026" data-caption="5.webp">    <img src="/img/post/过生日了喵/5.webp" alt="5.webp">  </a>  <a class="fancybox" href="/img/post/过生日了喵/6.webp" data-fancybox="birthday-2026" data-caption="6.webp">    <img src="/img/post/过生日了喵/6.webp" alt="6.webp">  </a>  <a class="fancybox" href="/img/post/过生日了喵/7.webp" data-fancybox="birthday-2026" data-caption="7.webp">    <img src="/img/post/过生日了喵/7.webp" alt="7.webp">  </a>  <a class="fancybox" href="/img/post/过生日了喵/8.webp" data-fancybox="birthday-2026" data-caption="8.webp">    <img src="/img/post/过生日了喵/8.webp" alt="8.webp">  </a>  <a class="fancybox" href="/img/post/过生日了喵/9.webp" data-fancybox="birthday-2026" data-caption="9.webp">    <img src="/img/post/过生日了喵/9.webp" alt="9.webp">  </a></div>]]></content>
    
    
    
